description:
Implement RendererKey - the lookup key for finding renderers in the registry.

Location: crates/baml-bridge/src/prompt/renderer.rs

```rust
/// Key for looking up renderers in the registry
#[derive(Debug, Clone, PartialEq, Eq, Hash)]
pub struct RendererKey {
    pub type_key: TypeKey,        // identifies the type
    pub style: &'static str,      // 'default', 'json', 'compact', etc.
}

/// Identifies a type for renderer lookup
#[derive(Debug, Clone, PartialEq, Eq, Hash)]
pub enum TypeKey {
    Class {
        name: String,
        mode: StreamingMode,      // from baml_types
    },
    Enum {
        name: String,
    },
    // Primitives don't need type-level renderers
}

impl RendererKey {
    pub fn for_class(name: impl Into<String>, mode: StreamingMode, style: &'static str) -> Self {
        Self {
            type_key: TypeKey::Class { name: name.into(), mode },
            style,
        }
    }

    pub fn for_enum(name: impl Into<String>, style: &'static str) -> Self {
        Self {
            type_key: TypeKey::Enum { name: name.into() },
            style,
        }
    }
}
```

The key must be hashable for use in IndexMap.
